INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (181,1,'2025-03-12 13:28:33','2025-03-12 13:28:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our dentistry program recommends eating apples as a natural way to promote oral health. To encourage healthy habits, we are excited to introduce \"Apple Day,\" where students can enjoy free, fresh apples throughout the day. Apples are not only delicious but also help clean teeth, strengthen gums, and stimulate saliva production, which reduces the risk of cavities. This initiative aims to raise awareness about the importance of nutrition in maintaining a healthy smile while providing students with a tasty and nutritious snack. By making apples easily accessible, we hope to inspire lifelong habits that benefit both dental health and overall well-being.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','An Apple a Day','Our dentistry program recommends eating apples.','publish','closed','closed','','an-apple-a-day','','','2025-03-12 13:28:33','2025-03-12 13:28:33','',0,'http://fictional-university.local/?post_type=slide&#038;p=181',0,'slide','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (183,1,'2025-03-12 13:29:51','2025-03-12 13:29:51','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fictional University offers lunch plans for those in need, ensuring that no student has to face hunger while pursuing their education. Through the Free Food initiative, all students have access to nutritious meals at no cost, removing financial barriers and promoting a supportive campus environment. This program not only addresses food insecurity but also fosters a sense of community by ensuring that everyone has the energy and focus needed to succeed academically. By prioritizing students\' well-being, Fictional University demonstrates its commitment to equity, inclusivity, and the holistic development of its student body. Free Food is more than just a meal—it’s a step toward a brighter, more equitable future for all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Free Food','Fictional University offers lunch plans for those in need.','publish','closed','closed','','free-food','','','2025-03-12 13:29:51','2025-03-12 13:29:51','',0,'http://fictional-university.local/?post_type=slide&#038;p=183',0,'slide','',0);
